{"tid":1118212,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果2019款iPhone模具曝光，三角形三攝穩了","createTime":"2019-04-21T08:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T14:35:51.000Z","uid":141060,"like":4,"dislike":207,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"54212bc02fdfb5d222d55ed07dcffcd6d90fb2a1","tid":1118212,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:54:51.000Z","msg":"4月21日消息蘋果產品爆料達人今天分享了兩張照片，疑似為2019款iPhone模具，照片中的模具是為了製作iPhone XI（暫定名）和iPhone XI Max 保護殼（暫定名）設計 的。 與之前的爆料相同，iPhone XI系列採用正方形突起，三攝不規則排列。<br />\n 根據此前供應鏈的消息，蘋果2019年款iPhone將採用三攝像頭設計，iPhone XI Max和iPhone XI將會新增一顆超廣角鏡頭，這顆超廣角鏡頭將會採用索尼獨家提供的1200萬像素攝像頭，像素 面積為1&mu;m，光圈大小為F/2.2。<br />\n 另外，蘋果這三款新iPhone的前置攝像頭都將升級為1200萬像素鏡頭。 分析師預測，為了讓鏡頭在外觀上不太明顯，蘋果新款iPhone後置超廣角鏡頭和前置鏡頭會採用黑鏡塗層技術。<br />\n 根據現階段曝光的模具，我們看到，2019款iPhone的主攝像頭很大概率使用的就是三攝像，而另外一個模具顯示，蘋果2019款iPhone背面攝像頭部分將會有五個開孔，除了三攝 和閃光燈開孔，不排除還會有ToF鏡頭。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6mv8NsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6mv8NsT.jpg&h=8e9aba88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nYe9wUz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnYe9wUz.jpg&h=6ef12ae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BQqHRUA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBQqHRUA.jpg&h=9202cc7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae8a83c597686cebd2281600ce537b9bf45748c8","tid":1118212,"uid":158977,"like":43,"dislike":49,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:55:19.000Z","msg":"成部華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f649589b63b6ceed365bdbaad27cee4cc2e1018","tid":1118212,"uid":61547,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:55:47.000Z","msg":"外星科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a4b932a7618448754976f79e6bdc7c68ebc126","tid":1118212,"uid":141060,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2